acceptance_criteria: pm <unknown> --help exits non-zero with the unknown-command error and suggestions (parity with pm <unknown>); known-command --help behavior unchanged; regression spec covers both the arbitrary-name and plausible-name (e.g. pm link --help) cases; GH-576 closed with evidence
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: Protected the existing unknown-command help behavior with arbitrary-name and plausible-name real-runtime regression coverage.
expected_result: Unknown command help probes exit non-zero with structured unknown-command diagnostics and suggestions.
actual_result: Both definitely-not-a-command --help and link --help exit 2 while known help behavior remains unchanged.
